yTime":"2017-10-17T07:15:25.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人為左家用斬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靠家用嘅廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d122939595cbf4b6fdbe7acc5634aa14dbe3ad35","tid":438664,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"廢老想要幾多家用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2e5aad40cd9a7649b20b94fc17f6b7a088af11","tid":438664,"uid":3180,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:06:45.000Z","msg":"都到收尾個幾年啦，仲家咩用呀"},{"pid":"8c8ae326b2d59441f40d00ab6180e864195c4e23","tid":438664,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b521723cdea55a79dcb35d7a7723e86eaa69c7fa","tid":438664,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"算好人，唔斬死個孫"},{"pid":"ffa387e9aadb0f7826d7d43442b39b30f058ab9b","tid":438664,"uid":113183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:53:56.000Z","msg":"辣殺"},{"pid":"addb8d742b5378f7a4f237011a559cfd0b0575d5","tid":438664,"uid":1712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:05:05.000Z","msg":"好彩佢冇去斬3歲嗰個"},{"pid":"a24ff596d9b9c5329a1d81544834535f2acc29cb","tid":438664,"uid":11254,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:06:53.000Z","msg":"所以話住公屋WOR <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你住埋我個份"},{"pid":"7b3d2105fe7b8fbb04ee538ce4c575f33e7483a4","tid":438664,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398a0e5f78651c621d30e3a19e87f07d1d374eaa","tid":438664,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:17:55.